III. Bugs
----------------------------------------------
1. It so far works for 1. Sometimes the GlassRobot does not drop off to the 1st conveyor correctly. If that happens restart.
2. The third piece won't get picked up by the GlassRobot.
3. The factory does not really work for multiple glasses at a time (more than 3). 
4. Sometimes stations are not performing as desired.
